<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFFF4FFAEFF1C70CEDA90F842" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FFF4FFAEFF1C70CEDA11F9E2" blockId="69.[151,757,1513,1985]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF4FFAEFF1C70CED97EF982" bold="true" box="[151,262,1513,1537]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">Comment</emphasis>
: The previously known distribution included 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF4FFAEFF1C732ED8AEF9A2" box="[151,214,1545,1569]" name="Nepal" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">Nepal</collectingCountry>
and North 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF4FFAEFED0732ED9EBF9A2" box="[347,403,1545,1569]" name="India" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">India</collectingCountry>
eastwards to 
<collectingRegion id="3C0203C2FFF4FFAEFDA6732EDA0FF9A2" box="[557,631,1545,1569]" country="India" name="Assam" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">Assam</collectingRegion>
. The above specimens represent the first record from 
<collectingRegion id="3C0203C2FFF4FFAEFD08730ED895F9E2" country="India" name="Arunachal Pradesh" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">Arunachal Pradesh</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFF77736ED9FEF9E2" author="ASSING, V." box="[252,390,1609,1633]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="5 - 20" refId="ref76140" refString="ASSING, V. 2003: A review of the Himalayan species of Amaurodera (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Entomological Problems 33 (1): 5 - 20." type="journal article" year="2003">ASSING 2003</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFE1B736ED9A9F9E2" author="ASSING, V." box="[400,465,1609,1633]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="1 - 12" refId="ref76174" refString="ASSING, V. 2005 a: A review of the Himalayan species of Amaurodera (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). II. New species and additional records. - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A (Biologie), Nr. 680: 1 - 12." type="journal article" year="2005">2005a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFE50736EDA68F9E2" author="ASSING, V." box="[475,528,1609,1633]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="201 - 226" refId="ref76536" refString="ASSING, V. 2009: New species and additional records of Lomechusini from the Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A, Neue Serie 2: 201 - 226." type="journal article" year="2009">2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFD90736EDA25F9E2" author="ASSING, V." box="[539,605,1609,1633]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="243 - 262" refId="ref76746" refString="ASSING, V. 2015 c: New species and additional records of Lomechusini from the Palaearctic region, primarily from China (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Contributions to Entomology 65 (2): 243 - 262." type="journal article" year="2015">2015c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FFF4FFAEFF1C734EDA90F842" blockId="69.[151,757,1513,1985]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFF1C734ED914F902" author="YAN, Z. - Q. &amp; LI, L. - Z." box="[151,364,1641,1665]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="272 - 278" refId="ref78449" refString="YAN, Z. - Q. &amp; LI, L. - Z. 2015 a: New species and additional records of Amaurodera FAUVEL in southern China (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Aleocharinae). - Zootaxa 3931 (2): 272 - 278." type="journal article" year="2015">YAN &amp; LI (2015a)</bibRefCitation>
suggest that 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF4FFAEFD84734EDAE9F902" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2003" box="[527,657,1641,1665]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Amaurodera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cameroni">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF4FFAEFD84734EDAE9F902" box="[527,657,1641,1665]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">A. cameroni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
may be conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF4FFAEFEEA73AEDAE0F922" authority="PACE, 1998" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1998" box="[353,664,1673,1697]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yunnanensis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF4FFAEFEEA73AEDA7DF922" box="[353,517,1673,1697]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">A. yunnanensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFD9F73AEDAE0F922" author="PACE, R." box="[532,664,1673,1697]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="911 - 982" refId="ref77804" refString="PACE, R. 1998: Aleocharinae della Cina: Parte IV (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 105 (4): 911 - 982." type="journal article" year="1998">PACE, 1998</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. In the latter, however, the ventral process of the aedeagus is much more convex subapically (lateral view), the crista apicalis of the aedeagus is longer, and the spermatheca differs by a shorter distal portion and a longer and terminally convex proximal portion of the capsule (
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF4FFAEFF2A726ED95BF8E2" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2003" box="[161,291,1865,1889]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Amaurodera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cameroni">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF4FFAEFF2A726ED95BF8E2" box="[161,291,1865,1889]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">A. cameroni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: proximal portion distinctly truncate). For illustrations of the intraspecific variation of the genitalia of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF4FFAEFF7972AED90CF822" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2003" box="[242,372,1929,1953]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Amaurodera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cameroni">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF4FFAEFF7972AED90CF822" box="[242,372,1929,1953]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">A. cameroni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
see 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFE2072AEDA37F822" author="ASSING, V." box="[427,591,1929,1953]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="5 - 20" refId="ref76140" refString="ASSING, V. 2003: A review of the Himalayan species of Amaurodera (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Entomological Problems 33 (1): 5 - 20." type="journal article" year="2003">ASSING (2003)</bibRefCitation>
, for figures of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF4FFAEFF1C728ED943F842" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1998" box="[151,315,1961,1985]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yunnanensis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF4FFAEFF1C728ED943F842" box="[151,315,1961,1985]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="82">A. yunnanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
see 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFEE1728EDA50F842" author="YAN, Z. - Q. &amp; LI, L. - Z." box="[362,552,1961,1985]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="272 - 278" refId="ref78449" refString="YAN, Z. - Q. &amp; LI, L. - Z. 2015 a: New species and additional records of Amaurodera FAUVEL in southern China (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Aleocharinae). - Zootaxa 3931 (2): 272 - 278." type="journal article" year="2015">YAN &amp; LI (2015a)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF4FFAEFDD6728EDA9CF842" author="PACE, R." box="[605,740,1961,1985]" pageId="69" pageNumber="82" pagination="911 - 982" refId="ref77804" refString="PACE, R. 1998: Aleocharinae della Cina: Parte IV (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 105 (4): 911 - 982." type="journal article" year="1998">PACE (1998)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
